So in order to connect the robot arm just follow those simple steps 


1- Import the Base and start working from it
2- Bring Waist and put it above the base so they are connected together
3- Connect Arm 01 with the Waist 
4- Connect Arm 02 with Arm 01 
5- Connect Waist 001 with Arm 02 so they are linked together proberly
6- Connect the Gripper with the Waist 001 

Now the robot arm is connected and you are good to go
